title: Give Some Good News
itunes:title: Give Some Good News
description:
Today on the show, after the tragic news of rapper Trouble passing away over the weekend we ran back the time Trouble stopped by the show and spoke about storytelling, who created trap music and more. Next they opened the phone lines to hear some good news about anything going on in our listeners lives, because of all the bad news recently. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the man who killed Trouble this weekend. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
